{"tid":1478880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣方向：破解中國人心理","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T06:36:04.000Z","uid":279962,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41b6716ce887d1c9e0b14966d1537132236bc8f1","tid":1478880,"uid":279962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">佢哋係有得食就得</span></strong></span><br />\n要贏 就要令佢地覺得<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係個政權搞9佢基本生活</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n背景 我屋企連著黑色都會被質問點解的 老豆藍到直情黑傾唔到所以算 咁啱貼緊誠哥廣告嗰陣同家母傾咗陣 so shocking...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:媽(典型順民)<br />\n<br />\n￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國進步緊，要俾啲時間佢<br />\n<br />\n￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港退步緊喎 (解釋送中已經係由法治變返人治啦 下刪一段而家發生緊乜事...)<br />\n<br />\n￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吓？！你問良心先 係咪進步咗好多 你都未經歷過冇得食嗰陣！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼(諗住講啲冇咁抽象)好似監控系統喎 係你一舉一動都信用評分 冇咗基本自由同人權...<br />\n<br />\n￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行得正企得正怕乜 大陸人而家咪生活得好好地<br />\n<br />\n￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家已經係莫須有罪名 行出街 買鐳射筆都俾人拉喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼咁你唔好買十支咁多吖嘛！我今日買咗一把刀都冇事。<br />\n<br />\n￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />....<br />\n<br />\n(最尾呢句先係重點)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">過唔到生活仲講咩？你呢啲乜乜自由同法治食得？</span></span><br />\n唔好再搞亂香港呀...<br />\n<br />\n破解中國人心理，佢地係由衷地認為感謝黨感謝國家賜我食物。你講呢啲良心呀公義呀自由呀係嘥氣架，佢地唔會有動力去爭取。掉咗天文數字落明日大嶼佢地冇所謂架，因為仲去到街市買餸有飯食，搞佢唔到。順民對唔食得嘅嘢適應力好高架。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以藍絲文宣，唔駛嘥氣講啲人話，講動物話就夠。嘩！你個(主人)政府唔俾你食飯呀！<br />\n<br />\n個idea係咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係要佢地冇得食先會出嚟！讀中國歷史差，但每個朝代嘅完結一定係啲人冇野食所以出嚟推翻政權，呢個係中國人特質。<br />\n<br />\nPS 818維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4686e828859ecdd616ba14bbd927f52aad9e98d5","tid":1478880,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>和理非係時候要進化喇! 818 同步搞! 後備持久戰plan! </strong><br />\n<br />\n［推上熱門！！！］全港新戰略‐和理非『節奏抗爭』每日9點準時敲擊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475606</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uybaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uybaW.jpg&h=ddfac6a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"631ac5f671d1ae7d7ea29fae8d49683fbfdb599e","tid":1478880,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"576d9e19645b76cd677857393439784f6620c6c1","tid":1478880,"uid":279962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"631ac5f671d1ae7d7ea29fae8d49683fbfdb599e","tid":1478880,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"其實真係要<br />\n<br />\n唔搞到佢冇飯開係唔會出嚟<br />\n<br />